Tagant n '''Harhura''' nɣ '''Lharhura''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: غابة الهرهورة) tga yat [[tagant]] iwalan i [[Tamnaḍt n Ṣṣxirat-Tmara|tmnaḍt n Ṣṣxirat-Tmara]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Rrbaṭ-Sla-Lqnḍrt|Rrbaṭ-Sla-Lqnḍrt]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Teṭṭaf tagant ad yat tajumma n 62 hiktar d tugt n imɣyan lli gis illan gan tn taddagin  n taydiwin.<ref name=":0">https://web.archive.org/web/20160305032419/http://skhiratemara.ma/def.asp?codelangue=23&info=1232&rubm1=1193</ref>

Tama n tagant ad ar nttafa ubraz abldi n tmdint n Tmara d ur akk taggug f taɣart, yan wasuk ka illan gratsn, illa ɣ ugns nns yan lmuxyyam iwalan i tamawast n tiɛɛurma d tunnunt ar t tstaɣllan timsmunin ɣ usnmala n id lmuxyyam n unbdu nɣ imuddutn ɣ usggʷas kullut.<ref name=":0" />

Tga tagant n Harhura yan unfus awnḍan bahra istawhman ɣ tsga, d ar sis tackan middn afad ad skrn imussutn izdin d tunnunt.<ref name=":0" />

